metadata.name: G.A.S. Series 2 #12 Shareef O'Neal - Legendary
metadata.description:
Shareef O’Neal, a 4-Star and ESPN 100 basketball recruit coming out of high school, made a name for himself on and off the court by triumphantly returning to collegiate basketball after undergoing open-heart surgery for an anomalous right coronary artery.

Now a member of the LSU Tigers (his Dad’s Alma Mater), Shareef has become an Ambassador for The American Heart Association and an inspiration to the world! Shareef needs a Rookie Card NFT!

G.A.S. Trading Cards is proud to present its 1st NFT!
